   "body" : "I tried to move the bitcoin data directory from \n\n```\nC:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Roaming\\Bitcoin\n```\n\nto another disk/partition, because my ssd was full. For this task I used the \"junction\" tool from microsoft. It creates a symbolic link between the source and target directory.\nhttp://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/sysinternals/bb896768.aspx\n\nAfter completing Bitcoin-qt does not start up any more. \n![unbenanntes bild](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/4135093/1962246/38f64680-8284-11e3-8254-9b9b4333a0b4.png)\n\nI'm sure the process of moving this directory is the reason for this fault. If i cancel the link it works fine again.\n",
